{"tid":207121,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[創業］網上藥房有冇得諗？","createTime":"2017-04-18T18:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:34:19.000Z","uid":32534,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60a6c2792a8539d12a98c008476128e7fd1d6018","tid":207121,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"想開間網上藥房，賣嘅嘢同一般藥房無異（中西成藥，日用品，保健品，condom,紙巾⋯除左處方藥），售錢會比萬寧屈臣氏平好多，同送埋上門。見好大公司d online store都好求其又冇咩promo。因為有親戚開藥房，貨源唔係問題，自己係it狗就grad,想試下網上創業，好初步既概念，唔知大家有冇咩意見一齊傾下？"},{"pid":"777d9db8e01bc13022ecf558b7abc08c169c26c2","tid":207121,"uid":106278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗拎牌？"},{"pid":"3a36e771f191f495a0d5fb33270438fc7d8aea70","tid":207121,"uid":32534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗拎牌？</blockquote><br />\n問過要個office商業登記，但唔賣處方毒藥戈個藥行牌就好易拎到。"},{"pid":"cb8a4bf20cb4c375a2318061cbd33f5399f54b74","tid":207121,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:45:13.000Z","msg":"Try"},{"pid":"c5eddd48cd7c34ad0f751dc461abc5ded080701c","tid":207121,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:45:30.000Z","msg":"係就快手 你上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541c8b6e4e57d75ecc59b7212c4bad6cedc49d92","tid":207121,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係就快手 你上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未畢業，仲有一個月，初步有個想法姐，想上黎集思廣益下"},{"pid":"169381216400ce5d867df5238fdd79e33a996f06","tid":207121,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:48:01.000Z","msg":"老果堆應該少用online shop 何況係藥<br />\n買果堆似年青人多<br />\nCondom 避孕藥 壯陽藥 <b